body:
OK I got a bit further this time. Wrote the tests for the object functions. Could you please do a quick review? Tests below.

Issues:
- Not sure what the guard does in defaults()
- Can't seem to get findKey working with pluck/where type callbacks. I'm thinking the where case is not viable but I thought I'd ask

```
_.findKey({ 'foo': 'bar' }, function(val) { return val === 'bar'; }) => 'foo' // ok
_.findKey({ 'foo': 'bar' }, 'bar') => undefined // ???
_.findKey({ 'foo': 'bar' }, { foo: 'bar' }) => undefined // ??
```

